spec_data.Name: python2-jaydebeapi
spec_data.Description:
The JayDeBeApi module allows you to connect from Python code to databases using
Java JDBC. It provides a Python DB-API v2.0 to that database.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 24 Aug 2017 07:24:39 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Bridge from JDBC database drivers to Python DB-API
